{
  "id": "RAW_3c3a6208",
  "title": "Gemini API 新篇章：Veo 3.1 震撼发布，创意功能全面升级",
  "url": "https://developers.googleblog.com/en/introducing-veo-3-1-and-new-creative-capabilities-in-the-gemini-api/",
  "date": "2025-10-15 00:00:00",
  "author": "Alisa Fortin, Luis Cobo, Guillaume Vernade",
  "siteName": "Google Developers Blog",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div class=\"block\">\n   <img class=\"banner-image\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-developer-goog-blog-assets/images/Veo3.1_Wagtial_Banner.original.png\" alt=\"Veo3.1_Wagtial_Banner\">\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <p data-block-key=\"7dpka\"><b>Today, we are releasing Veo 3.1 and Veo 3.1 Fast in paid preview in the</b> <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/video?example=dialogue\"><b>Gemini API</b></a><b>.</b> This updated model offers several improvements, as well as improved outputs when generating video from images. These new models are available via the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/video?example=dialogue\">Gemini API</a> in <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/apps/bundled/veo_studio?fullscreenApplet=true\">Google AI Studio</a> and <a href=\"http://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/studio/media\">Vertex AI</a>. Veo 3.1 is also available in the <a href=\"https://gemini.google.com/\">Gemini app</a> and <a href=\"http://flow.google/\">Flow</a>.</p>\n    <h3 data-block-key=\"9t2l9\" id=\"veo-3.1:-our-improved-video-generation-model\"><b>Veo 3.1: our improved video generation model</b></h3>\n    <p data-block-key=\"j59v\">Veo 3.1 and Veo 3.1 Fast empower developers to create more engaging content through significant upgrades. The models now generate <b>richer native audio</b>, from natural conversations to synchronized sound effects, and offer <b>greater narrative control</b> with an improved understanding of cinematic styles. <b>Enhanced image-to-video</b> capabilities ensure better prompt adherence while delivering superior audio and visual quality and maintaining character consistency across multiple scenes.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content yt-video\">\n    <div class=\"glue-video\">\n     <div class=\"glue-video__container glue-video__container--inline\" data-glue-yt-video-vid=\"orcRl82lGLc\" id=\"youtube-player-671277\">\n      <iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/orcRl82lGLc?enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.googleblog.com&amp;widgetid=1&amp;forigin=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.googleblog.com%2Fen%2Fintroducing-veo-3-1-and-new-creative-capabilities-in-the-gemini-api%2F&amp;aoriginsup=1&amp;vf=1\" id=\"widget2\" data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=\"true\"></iframe>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"glue-video__nojs\">\n      <p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=orcRl82lGLc\">Link to Youtube Video</a> (visible only when JS is disabled)</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <p data-block-key=\"xwm4e\">In addition to the model update, we are introducing new model capabilities, including using reference images to guide video generation, extend existing Veo videos, and generate transitions between a first and last frame.</p>\n    <h4 data-block-key=\"42ddh\" id=\"guide-generation-with-'ingredients-to-video'\"><b>Guide generation with ‘Ingredients to video’</b></h4>\n    <p data-block-key=\"9f8ll\">You can now guide the generation process by providing up to 3 reference images of a character, object, or scene. This is helpful for maintaining character consistency across multiple shots or applying a specific style to your video.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content\">\n    <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n     <img class=\"regular-image\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-developer-goog-blog-assets/images/Screenshot_2025-10-14_9.45.50_AM.original.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-10-14 9.45.50 AM\">\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content yt-video\">\n    <div class=\"glue-video\">\n     <div class=\"glue-video__container glue-video__container--inline\" data-glue-yt-video-vid=\"h9efowrW9ik\" id=\"youtube-player-34405\">\n      <iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/h9efowrW9ik?enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.googleblog.com&amp;widgetid=3&amp;forigin=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.googleblog.com%2Fen%2Fintroducing-veo-3-1-and-new-creative-capabilities-in-the-gemini-api%2F&amp;aoriginsup=1&amp;vf=1\" id=\"widget4\" data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=\"true\"></iframe>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"glue-video__nojs\">\n      <p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=h9efowrW9ik\">Link to Youtube Video</a> (visible only when JS is disabled)</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content code-block line-numbers\">\n    <pre class=\"language-python line-numbers\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> google <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> genai\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> google<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>genai <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> types\n\n\nclient <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> genai<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Client<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\noperation <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>models<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>generate_videos<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    model<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"veo-3.1-generate-preview\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    prompt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>prompt<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    config<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>types<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>GenerateVideosConfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        reference_images<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>reference_image1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> reference_image2<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre>\n    <div class=\"language-block glue-font-weight-medium\">Python</div>\n    <div class=\"copy-code-block\">\n     <button class=\"copy-clipboard\">\n      <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\" width=\"24px\" fill=\"#202124\">\n       <path d=\"M360-240q-33 0-56.5-23.5T280-320v-480q0-33 23.5-56.5T360-880h360q33 0 56.5 23.5T800-800v480q0 33-23.5 56.5T720-240H360Zm0-80h360v-480H360v480ZM200-80q-33 0-56.5-23.5T120-160v-560h80v560h440v80H200Zm160-240v-480 480Z\"></path>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dark-mode-block\">\n     <button class=\"dark-mode-toggle\">\n      <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\" width=\"24px\" fill=\"#202124\">\n       <path d=\"M480-120q-150 0-255-105T120-480q0-150 105-255t255-105q14 0 27.5 1t26.5 3q-41 29-65.5 75.5T444-660q0 90 63 153t153 63q55 0 101-24.5t75-65.5q2 13 3 26.5t1 27.5q0 150-105 255T480-120Zm0-80q88 0 158-48.5T740-375q-20 5-40 8t-40 3q-123 0-209.5-86.5T364-660q0-20 3-40t8-40q-78 32-126.5 102T200-480q0 116 82 198t198 82Zm-10-270Z\"></path>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <p data-block-key=\"9tczb\">See more in the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/video#multiple-images\">documentation</a>.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <h4 data-block-key=\"7nyio\" id=\"create-longer-videos-with-'scene-extension'\"><b>Create longer videos with ‘Scene extension’</b></h4>\n    <p data-block-key=\"848lu\">Your story is no longer limited by the original generation. With Scene extension, you can create longer videos, even lasting for a minute or more, by generating new clips that connect to your previous video. Each new video is generated based on the final second of the previous clip. This maintains visual continuity, making the feature ideal for extending shots with background audio.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content yt-video\">\n    <div class=\"glue-video\">\n     <div class=\"glue-video__container glue-video__container--inline\" data-glue-yt-video-vid=\"_Fpl8SuQC4c\" id=\"youtube-player-948571\">\n      <iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/_Fpl8SuQC4c?enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.googleblog.com&amp;widgetid=5&amp;forigin=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.googleblog.com%2Fen%2Fintroducing-veo-3-1-and-new-creative-capabilities-in-the-gemini-api%2F&amp;aoriginsup=1&amp;vf=1\" id=\"widget6\" data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=\"true\"></iframe>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"glue-video__nojs\">\n      <p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_Fpl8SuQC4c\">Link to Youtube Video</a> (visible only when JS is disabled)</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"video-description\">Extended</div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content code-block line-numbers\">\n    <pre class=\"language-python line-numbers\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> google <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> genai\n\n\nclient <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> genai<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Client<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\noperation <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>models<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>generate_videos<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    model<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"veo-3.1-generate-preview\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    prompt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>prompt<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    video<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>video_to_extend\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre>\n    <div class=\"language-block glue-font-weight-medium\">Python</div>\n    <div class=\"copy-code-block\">\n     <button class=\"copy-clipboard\">\n      <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\" width=\"24px\" fill=\"#202124\">\n       <path d=\"M360-240q-33 0-56.5-23.5T280-320v-480q0-33 23.5-56.5T360-880h360q33 0 56.5 23.5T800-800v480q0 33-23.5 56.5T720-240H360Zm0-80h360v-480H360v480ZM200-80q-33 0-56.5-23.5T120-160v-560h80v560h440v80H200Zm160-240v-480 480Z\"></path>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dark-mode-block\">\n     <button class=\"dark-mode-toggle\">\n      <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\" width=\"24px\" fill=\"#202124\">\n       <path d=\"M480-120q-150 0-255-105T120-480q0-150 105-255t255-105q14 0 27.5 1t26.5 3q-41 29-65.5 75.5T444-660q0 90 63 153t153 63q55 0 101-24.5t75-65.5q2 13 3 26.5t1 27.5q0 150-105 255T480-120Zm0-80q88 0 158-48.5T740-375q-20 5-40 8t-40 3q-123 0-209.5-86.5T364-660q0-20 3-40t8-40q-78 32-126.5 102T200-480q0 116 82 198t198 82Zm-10-270Z\"></path>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <p data-block-key=\"hc02i\">See more in the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/video#using-first-and-last-video-frames\">documentation</a>.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <h4 data-block-key=\"ntaj9\" id=\"control-your-video-with-'first-and-last-frame'\"><b>Control your video with ‘First and last frame’</b></h4>\n    <p data-block-key=\"bcobd\">Create smooth, natural scenes that bridge two different images. By providing a starting and an ending image, you can direct Veo 3.1 to generate the transition between them, complete with accompanying audio.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content\">\n    <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n     <img class=\"regular-image\" src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gweb-developer-goog-blog-assets/images/Screenshot_2025-10-13_4.09.05_PM.original.png\" alt=\"Screenshot 2025-10-13 4.09.05 PM\">\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content yt-video\">\n    <div class=\"glue-video\">\n     <div class=\"glue-video__container glue-video__container--inline\" data-glue-yt-video-vid=\"Kew48V17NWM\" id=\"youtube-player-664868\">\n      <iframe frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" title=\"YouTube video player\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Kew48V17NWM?enablejsapi=1&amp;origin=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.googleblog.com&amp;widgetid=7&amp;forigin=https%3A%2F%2Fdevelopers.googleblog.com%2Fen%2Fintroducing-veo-3-1-and-new-creative-capabilities-in-the-gemini-api%2F&amp;aoriginsup=1&amp;vf=1\" id=\"widget8\" data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=\"true\"></iframe>\n     </div>\n     <div class=\"glue-video__nojs\">\n      <p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Kew48V17NWM\">Link to Youtube Video</a> (visible only when JS is disabled)</p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content code-block line-numbers\">\n    <pre class=\"language-python line-numbers\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-python\"><span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> google <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> genai\n<span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> google<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>genai <span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> types\n\nclient <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> genai<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>Client<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\noperation <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> client<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>models<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>generate_videos<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    model<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"veo-3.1-generate-preview\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    prompt<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>prompt<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    image<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>first_frame<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    config<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>types<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>GenerateVideosConfig<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n        last_frame<span class=\"token operator\">=</span>last_frame<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre>\n    <div class=\"language-block glue-font-weight-medium\">Python</div>\n    <div class=\"copy-code-block\">\n     <button class=\"copy-clipboard\">\n      <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\" width=\"24px\" fill=\"#202124\">\n       <path d=\"M360-240q-33 0-56.5-23.5T280-320v-480q0-33 23.5-56.5T360-880h360q33 0 56.5 23.5T800-800v480q0 33-23.5 56.5T720-240H360Zm0-80h360v-480H360v480ZM200-80q-33 0-56.5-23.5T120-160v-560h80v560h440v80H200Zm160-240v-480 480Z\"></path>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"dark-mode-block\">\n     <button class=\"dark-mode-toggle\">\n      <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" height=\"24px\" viewBox=\"0 -960 960 960\" width=\"24px\" fill=\"#202124\">\n       <path d=\"M480-120q-150 0-255-105T120-480q0-150 105-255t255-105q14 0 27.5 1t26.5 3q-41 29-65.5 75.5T444-660q0 90 63 153t153 63q55 0 101-24.5t75-65.5q2 13 3 26.5t1 27.5q0 150-105 255T480-120Zm0-80q88 0 158-48.5T740-375q-20 5-40 8t-40 3q-123 0-209.5-86.5T364-660q0-20 3-40t8-40q-78 32-126.5 102T200-480q0 116 82 198t198 82Zm-10-270Z\"></path>\n      </svg>\n     </button>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <p data-block-key=\"suxry\">See more in the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/video#using-first-and-last-video-frames\">documentation</a>.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <p data-block-key=\"mp6wm\"><b>What people are building with Veo 3.1</b></p>\n    <p data-block-key=\"2ahmr\"><a href=\"https://www.promise.ai/\">Promise Studios</a>, a GenAI movie studio, uses Veo 3.1 within its MUSE Platform to enhance generative storyboarding and previsualization for director-driven storytelling at production quality.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <p data-block-key=\"mp6wm\"><a href=\"https://latitude.io/\">Latitude</a> is experimenting with Veo 3.1 in its generative narrative engine to instantly bring user-created stories to life.</p>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"inner-block-content rich-content\">\n    <h3 data-block-key=\"e5rqe\" id=\"start-building-today\"><b>Start building today</b></h3>\n    <p data-block-key=\"auqgi\">Veo 3.1 and these new capabilities are now available in paid preview via the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/video\">Gemini API</a>.</p>\n    <ul>\n     <li data-block-key=\"dijcb\">Dive into the <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/video\">documentation</a> for detailed parameter information and video length control,</li>\n     <li data-block-key=\"e122f\">Start using Veo 3.1 and the new features in <a href=\"https://aistudio.google.com/apps/bundled/veo_studio?fullscreenApplet=true\">Veo Studio</a>, our new AI Studio demo app (paid Gemini API key required)</li>\n     <li data-block-key=\"f62qj\">Or jump right into the code with the updated <a href=\"https://colab.research.google.com/github/google-gemini/cookbook/blob/main/quickstarts/Get_started_Veo.ipynb\">cookbook</a> guide</li>\n    </ul>\n    <p data-block-key=\"5rd48\">Veo 3.1 is the same <a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/pricing#veo-3.1\">price</a> as Veo 3. We are incredibly excited to see what you will build with these new capabilities!</p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Google 发布 Veo 3.1 和 Veo 3.1 Fast，通过更丰富的原生音频、电影级控制和引导式生成、场景扩展、帧过渡等创意功能，增强视频生成能力。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Google 发布 Veo 3.1 和 Veo 3.1 Fast，通过更丰富的原生音频、电影级控制和引导式生成、场景扩展、帧过渡等创意功能，增强视频生成能力。",
  "summary": "本文宣布通过 Gemini API、Google AI Studio 和 Vertex AI 以付费预览版发布 Veo 3.1 和 Veo 3.1 Fast。Veo 3.1 显著改进了视频生成，提供了更丰富的原生音频，包括自然的对话和同步的音效，并通过增强对电影风格的理解，提供更大的叙事控制。图像到视频的功能也得到了改进，确保更好地遵守提示并保持场景中的角色一致性。除了核心模型升级之外，还引入了新的功能：“Ingredients to video”允许使用最多三个参考图像来指导生成，以实现角色或风格的一致性；“Scene extension”通过将新片段连接到现有片段来创建更长的视频，同时保持视觉连续性；“First and last frame”有助于实现不同图像间平滑自然的音频过渡。文章重点介绍了 Promise Studios 和 Latitude 的早期采用，展示了模型在故事生成和互动叙事方面的潜力，鼓励开发人员开始使用新功能进行构建，并提供文档和代码示例的链接。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Veo 3.1 在视频生成质量和控制方面提供了显著改进。",
      "explanation": "更新后的模型生成更丰富的原生音频，通过改进对电影风格的理解提供更大的叙事控制，并通过更好地理解提示，并确保角色一致性，从而提升图像到视频的生成质量。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“Ingredients to video”：参考图像引导视频生成",
      "explanation": "开发人员可以提供最多三个参考图像来保持角色一致性或应用特定风格，从而提供对输出视频的更多创意控制。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“Scene extension”允许创建更长、视觉上连续的视频叙事。",
      "explanation": "此功能基于先前视频的最后一秒生成新的片段，从而在保持视觉连续性和背景音频的同时，扩展故事或镜头。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“First and last frame”有助于在不同图像之间实现无缝过渡。",
      "explanation": "通过提供开始和结束图像，Veo 3.1 可以生成中间视频帧和随附的音频，从而创建平滑自然的场景过渡。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Veo 3.1 可通过多个 Google 平台获得，从而为开发人员和工作室提供支持。",
      "explanation": "该模型可通过 Gemini API、Google AI Studio 和 Vertex AI 访问，Promise Studios 和 Latitude 等工作室的早期应用，验证了其在故事生成和预演方面的价值。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "今天，我们以 Gemini API 中的付费预览版发布 Veo 3.1 和 Veo 3.1 Fast。",
    "这些模型现在生成更丰富的原生音频，从自然的对话到同步的音效，并通过改进对电影风格的理解，提供更大的叙事控制。",
    "现在，您可以通过提供最多 3 张角色、物体或场景的参考图片来引导视频生成。",
